com.simiacryptus.mindseye.eval

Class BasicTrainable

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.simiacryptus.mindseye.lang.ReferenceCountingBase
      • com.simiacryptus.mindseye.eval.BasicTrainable
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DataTrainable, Trainable, TrainableDataMask, ReferenceCounting

    public class BasicTrainable
extends ReferenceCountingBase
implements DataTrainable, TrainableDataMask
    This class handles dispatching network evaluations, and distributing the evaluations to the system GPU(s). This is the main class the handles actual execution for training purposes.
